reviewText: I thought the audio of the DVD would be available in English but it is only in Polish with only English or Spanish subtitiles. The story is good.
I saw this film over 50 years ago. It is amusing, gripping and quite simply and conservatively religious without being over much so.
Both DVDs were great, good quality. Fast shipping. Brand new DVDs, wrapped in their plastic and everything. Happy buyer.
Very good condition.  Great buy.  Two in one.  I loved them both.  I saw this as a child and I think little children should see this and how much Jesus loves them.
